Description:
    Generates the API controller and the three basic views based on the model name provided

Example:
    rails generate API {Model}

    This will create:
	/app/controllers/api/v1/{Name}_controller.rb
	/app/views/api/v1/{Name}/
	/app/views/api/v1/{Name}/_{Name}.json.jbuilder
	/app/views/api/v1/{Name}/index.json.jbuilder
	/app/views/api/v1/{Name}/show.json.jbuilder
